{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243070/extras/giffusionv4.gif?t=1701619745\" /><br>Kodama Battles is a singleplayer autobattler/autochess with roguelite deckbuilder elements in a chill setting.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Build your team:</strong> Collect, place and upgrade Kodamas to build a powerful team. Kodamas have 3 levels (1,2 then 3 Stars). Many also have a last level making them fuse with another one to create a Mega Kodama.<br><br></li><li><strong>Double battlefield:</strong> Teams are separated into an attack and a defense squad for each battle. Mindful team management is required to attack effectively while leaving enough defenses to survive.<br><br></li><li><strong>Unique abilities:</strong> Most Kodamas have one straightforward but impactful ability. Mega Kodamas have game changing abilities.<br><br></li><li><strong>Combos:</strong> Impactful and diverse abilities lead to many many synergies and counters. Experiment to find new ways to play.<br><br></li><li><strong>Scaling difficulty:</strong> Unlock new difficulties upon run completion. The first difficulty is suitable for anyone. But meticulous team management and positioning are required to best the higher difficulties.<br><br></li><li><strong>Playstyle defining paths:</strong> The paths chosen bring further customization (modify drop rates, add positioning options...) and will lead to an unique build each run.<br><br></li><li><strong>Strategize peacefully:</strong> The calm of a lunar illuminated woodland is perfect to relax and strategize.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Kodama Battles!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2243070/814f22ef388852d2b44a12bfa9d6d6d5262c01ca.jpg"},{"name":"First teachings","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2243070/d9d542bbe66fc458859864aa44958a1795f14a4d.jpg"},{"n